title: Bug 7752 - Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
OB: When exporting multiple files with the same name from different directories to a zip file, the export fails.
EB: The zip file should be able to store files with the same name under different directories.
SR: To reproduce: 1. Create multiple files with the same name but located in different directories. 2. Attempt to export the files to a zip file.
